      "description": "A budget-friendly opportunity with strong value for the right buyer. This vehicle shows its age and is best suited for someone looking for straightforward transportation, a second car, or a solid project to make their own. Offered as an honest, affordable option with plenty of usefulness left for someone who appreciates a practical deal.",
