    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option for someone who wants an affordable runaround, a first project, or a handy spare vehicle. It\u2019s got character, and for the right buyer, there\u2019s still plenty of life and usefulness here. Priced to sell and worth a look if you want something simple, approachable, and easy on the wallet.",
