      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with strong bones and great potential. The powertrain pulls cleanly, steering feels direct, and it offers the kind of honest mechanical character that makes it a great starter project, commuter, or weekend tinkering platform. Cosmetic wear and age-related blemishes are present, but it remains a straightforward, usable car that can be driven and improved over time. Hard to find at this price point with this much upside.",
